HEADWORD: McCarthyism
<hw>McCarthyism</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <ety>[from <person>Senator
Joseph <etsep>McCarthy</etsep></person>, who repeatedly asserted without
evidence that numerous communists were present in the United States
government.]</ety> <def>Unscrupulously accusing people of disloyalty (as
by saying they were Communists).</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

